2026-05-13 | Find Mother Vertex in Directed Graph

Question
Find the mother vertex of the graph.
	Key Insight
In DFS:
		the last finished vertex
		is a potential mother vertex  
Why?
If a mother vertex exists,
it must finish last in DFS traversal.
	Approach
1.	Build adjacency list  
2.	Run DFS for all unvisited nodes:
		store last starting vertex  
3.	This last vertex becomes candidate  
4.	Run DFS again from candidate:
		if all vertices visited:
			candidate is valid
		else:
			no mother vertex exists  
5.	To get smallest mother vertex:
		check all vertices smaller than candidate too
	Time Complexity
	O(V + E)
	Space Complexity
	O(V + E)
	Solution
class Solution {
public:
    void dfs(int node,
             vector<vector<int>>& adj,
             vector<bool>& vis){
        vis[node] = true;
        for(int nei : adj[node]){
            if(!vis[nei]){
                dfs(nei, adj, vis);
            }
        }
    }
    int findMotherVertex(int V, vector<vector<int>>& edges) {
        vector<vector<int>> adj(V);
        for(auto &e : edges){
            adj[e[0]].push_back(e[1]);
        }
        vector<bool> vis(V, false);
        int candidate = -1;
        // find candidate
        for(int i = 0; i < V; i++){
            if(!vis[i]){
                dfs(i, adj, vis);
                candidate = i;
            }
        }
        // verify candidate
        fill(vis.begin(), vis.end(), false);
        dfs(candidate, adj, vis);
        for(bool x : vis){
            if(!x) return -1;
        }
        // smallest mother vertex
        for(int i = 0; i < candidate; i++){
            fill(vis.begin(), vis.end(), false);
            dfs(i, adj, vis);
            bool ok = true;
            for(bool x : vis){
                if(!x){
                    ok = false;
                    break;
                }
            }
            if(ok) return i;
        }
        return candidate;
    }
};
	Key Insight
The last DFS finishing vertex is the only possible candidate.  
Then:
		verify reachability  
This is a classic application of:
		DFS finishing order property.
